# Dependency Policy

## Adding
- Check stdlib/existing deps first. Evaluate: maintenance, downloads, license, size, transitives.
- Prefer small focused packages. Justify in PR description.

## Pinning
- Exact versions in production (no ^/~). Commit lockfiles (`uv.lock`, `package-lock.json`).

## Auditing
- `npm audit` / `pip audit` in CI. High/critical vulns block merges. Monthly update reviews.

## Banned
- No deps for stdlib functionality. No deps with unpatched CVEs. No deps unmaintained 2+ years.
